mods.abstract: Genre/Subject Matter:This black and white photograph shows Muscat from one side of the bay, with Jiwani Fort on the left hand side of the image, and on the right hand side of the image the British Political Agency, the hospital and Assistant Surgeon’s quarters, and the Telegraphs and Customs buildings.Inscriptions:Printed label on the reverse of the image: ‘No.6. Muscat, Agency with Jiwani Fort.’
